This month a MMORPG version of Dreamlords Resurrection will be published by Paradox Interactive. The game is developed by Lockpick Entertainment.

Now you have the opportunity to play Dreamlords Resurrection online with your friends. As a semi-divine Dreamlord, it falls to you to inspire and lead a band of struggling followers to found a strong and thriving city. Then, conquer new lands, defend against the Nightmares that roam the wilderness, and forge alliances with other newly-awakened Dreamlords.

In your struggles against monsters and other players, you will research new troop types and technologies, gather resources, and acquire and craft equipment for yourself and your army. And if you wish, you may pay Tribute to the gods, that you might receive their divine gifts and blessings, and that their wrath may rain down upon your enemies.

